Lesson 34 单词句型讲解

+ sleep         睡觉
+ shave         刮胡子
+ shaver        剃须刀
+ cry           哭
    The baby is crying.
+ wash          洗
+ wait          等待
    wait for me         等等我
    look at
    listen to




